      "content": "The manual counter is a good idea, I'll try implementing that. One thing though—the way you're describing these leaks as \"creatures\" and \"goblins\" is a bit unexpected. Are you using those as specific technical metaphors for certain types of memory corruption, or is there a reason for the fantasy framing?",
